---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { localAreaPagesEn } from '../../data/local-area-pages';
import { buildBreadcrumbSchema, buildCollectionPageSchema, buildWebSiteSchema } from '../../lib/seo';

const schemas = [
  buildWebSiteSchema(),
  buildCollectionPageSchema({
    name: 'Service Areas | Clinique du VR',
    description: 'Service areas covered by Clinique du VR from Gatineau for RV inspection, maintenance, and repair.',
    path: '/en/service-areas/'
  }),
  buildBreadcrumbSchema([
    { name: 'Home', path: '/en/' },
    { name: 'Service Areas' }
  ])
];
---

<Layout
  title="RV Service Areas | Gatineau, Ottawa, Outaouais, Laurentides | Clinique du VR"
  description="See the service areas covered by Clinique du VR from Gatineau for inspection, maintenance, and repair of RVs, travel trailers, and caravans."
  lang="en-CA"
  canonicalPath="/en/service-areas/"
  frPath="/zones-desservies/"
  enPath="/en/service-areas/"
  schemas={schemas}
>
  <Header lang="en" />

  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Local SEO</p>
        <h1>Service areas around Gatineau</h1>
        <p class="lead">Our workshop is based in Gatineau. We also support requests coming from Ottawa, Outaouais, and the Laurentides depending on the type of work, the issue involved, and whether the next step should happen in the workshop or through mobile support.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="areas-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="areas-grid">
          {localAreaPagesEn.map((page) => (
            <a class="area-card" href={`/en/areas/${page.slug}/`}>
              <p class="area-name">{page.area}</p>
              <h2>{page.h1}</h2>
              <p>{page.intro}</p>
              <span>View local page</span>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="content-grid">
          <article class="content-card">
            <h2>When a local page helps most</h2>
            <p>A local page is useful when you are searching for a specific service with a clear geographic context: water leak help in Gatineau, maintenance in Outaouais, repair support for Ottawa, or trailer water intrusion questions in the Laurentides.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="content-card">
            <h2>Gatineau workshop, regional support</h2>
            <p>The workshop in Gatineau remains the anchor point. Depending on the service request, we can direct you toward inspection, maintenance, or repair and confirm the most useful next step before travel or booking.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="content-card">
            <h2>Before you book</h2>
            <p>If you are still unsure which service fits best, start with our guidance page or contact us with a few photos of the RV, your city, the type of issue, and the urgency level.</p>
            <p class="actions"><a href="/en/choose-service/">Which service should you choose?</a> · <a href="/en/contact/">Contact the workshop</a></p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { padding: 4.5rem 0 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-navy-dark) 0%, #1f476d 60%, #eef3f7 60%, #eef3f7 100%); color: white; }
  .eyebrow { display: inline-flex; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding: 0.45rem 0.85rem; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: var(--brand-gold); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .page-hero h1 { color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 14ch; }
  .lead { max-width: 64ch; color: #e7edf4; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .areas-section { padding: 4rem 0; background: #eef3f7; }
  .areas-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .area-card { background: white; border-radius: 18px; padding: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(20, 36, 55, 0.08); }
  .area-name { color: var(--brand-green-dark); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-size: 0.82rem; }
  .area-card h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0.45rem 0 0.8rem; }
  .area-card p { color: var(--brand-muted); }
  .area-card span { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .content-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .content-card { background: white; border-radius: 18px; padding: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(20, 36, 55, 0.08); }
  .content-card p { margin-top: 0.75rem; color: var(--brand-muted); }
  .actions { font-weight: 700; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--brand-navy-dark) 0%, #1f476d 100%); padding: 3.8rem 0 2.8rem; } }
</style>
